##
## Future
##
@node Future "Future of DFB"

 Firstly, DFB is not perfect. Since this is the premiere release I am sure
 there are bugs in here but don't worry there has been a lot of betatesting
 and if there are any they will probably be minor. So what do I plan to
 do for DFB in the future?
 
 * Utilities, E.g: Top Up/Downloaders, File list generator.
 * XPR transfer protocol libraries. This way DFB will support more protocols
   such as Super Zmodem, Bimodem etc...
 * Speed ups, some speed ups which should launch the speed of DFB out of
   this world 
 * Ability to change the colours of the file list. This is practically done
   already! More cosmetic changes as well, file layout editor.
 * Daily download limits
 * More error messages and other stuff
 * Fix the hotkeys in the GUIs (The menu ones work but not the others)
 * Some minor enhancements
 * Can't think of anything else. All of the features I could think of are
   already in it!

@endnode

